title: Cant click anything ingame?
body: I recently just queued up for ranked, only to lose lp after they remade. i loaded in perfectly fine like the loading screen was smooth and everything but the moment i get in game i am unable to click anything, no keys work, i can see my cursor but it isnt the league cursor, i tried opening shop, even leveling up skills but nothing is working, any ideas why? Thank in advance, right now in a custom and still having the same problem, unable to move :/ or do anything

replies.body:
https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/F1goweJo-unable-to-use-keyboard-or-mouse-in-game-discord

tl;dr Turn off Discord overlay for the moment :)
Thank you so much :) Seras Dragon
